{"tid":848443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食安中心警告 別相信TXB大灣區弱智節目 食鯇魚魚生","createTime":"2018-10-05T02:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T04:18:48.000Z","uid":54373,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9705b6961fcb55030aed9de744b4d2784872d3","tid":848443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:31:31.000Z","msg":"切勿進食淡水魚生<br />\n<br />\n最近有電視節目介紹用鯇魚製作魚生，引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n在一般環境下飼養的淡水魚(例如鯇魚及大頭魚)，除了致病菌外，還可能帶有寄生蟲，例如可造成膽管梗阻、肝硬化和引致膽管癌的中華肝吸蟲。酒、醋、日式芥辣、黃芥辣及香料均不能殺死包括中華肝吸蟲在內的寄生蟲。<br />\n<br />\n市民無論是在港或外遊，切勿進食生或未徹底煮熟的淡水魚。在吃火鍋或粥品時，須待魚熟透方可進食。為保障公眾健康，根據《食物業規例》(第132X章)，本港禁售中式魚生。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n食物安全焦點 -- 淡水魚生中的中華肝吸蟲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/multimedia/multimedia_pub/multimedia_pub_fsf_52_01.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cfs.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fmultimedia%2Fmultimedia_pub%2Fmultimedia_pub_fsf_52_01.html&d=%2Bmo84QD1zui%2BOBj9n2G7c5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e3a43881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cfs.gov.hk/tc_chi/multimedia/multimedia_pub/multimedia_pub_fsf_52_01.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#食物安全  #食物安全中心  #淡水魚生  #鯇魚魚生"},{"pid":"f3e98951284a8e0eb0ef519481a5adf860fbab48","tid":848443,"uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.icdrama.se/images/film/big-big-bay-3ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.icdrama.se%2Fimages%2Ffilm%2Fbig-big-bay-3ef7.jpg&h=655ba6ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d868094885e0352c4f8c37c28cb679483eb7cf5","tid":848443,"uid":53466,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:36:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f18deccee217e60657139e6d6d1785c80f26ae4","tid":848443,"uid":71218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"其實我都覺得離譜,淡水魚好撚多蟲,重生食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a392b8af0358a79dbcc7e5dd332b5a45f64194","tid":848443,"uid":101945,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"弱智上去食死仲好<br />\n減少香港弱智人口"},{"pid":"c5bae6c3cb1aa1a0eda44cbd6873f564cec95ff7","tid":848443,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NY8JQhg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNY8JQhg.gif&h=75d0cc81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e8e51687aa90833e4cb7f2102502c35bef35052","tid":848443,"uid":132859,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒<br />\n寄生蟲不就是很肥美嗎<br />\n會有啥事呢？<br />\n<br />\n在肛門揪出來扒了皮<br />\n再滾一滾吃下去<br />\n就是人間美味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99f1ff88926e28e36530157bb3f313f7802c368","tid":848443,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"食安中心竟然以為自己可以干預到自然界最高法則natural selection，未免有啲自以為是<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e928f61d3cc7741630f429c230a7b8e902e321d","tid":848443,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"美橫BB有份食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34acc116a63293c32f1f716db6eb0b2ad4d91094","tid":848443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e928f61d3cc7741630f429c230a7b8e902e321d","tid":848443,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"美橫BB有份食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":